      "rationale": "Titanium alloy (Ti-6Al-4V) modeled with bilinear elastoplastic constitutive law calibrated to tensile coupon data. Geometric nonlinearity (large displacement formulation) enabled to capture screw bending beyond yield. UHMWPE test block modeled as linear elastic. Augmented Lagrange contact between screw and block interfaces. Model form choices consistent with published literature and ASTM F1717 simulation guidance."
