      "rationale": "Ti-6Al-4V elastic modulus (114 GPa), yield strength (880 MPa), and tangent modulus (1.8 GPa) derived from tensile coupon testing of same material lot as test constructs. Screw geometry digitized via CMM to ±0.01 mm. UHMWPE block modulus (1.0 GPa) from literature with sensitivity analysis confirming < 1% QoI sensitivity. Friction coefficient (0.15) from pin-on-disk tribology measurement."
