      "rationale": "Eleven non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw constructs assembled from production-lot components. All constructs dimensionally inspected via CMM prior to testing; all within drawing tolerances. Material certificates confirm same Ti-6Al-4V lot used for model material property calibration. Sample size exceeds minimum N=5 per FDA guidance for this device class."
