      "rationale": "Testing conducted at a single loading rate (5 mm/min) per ASTM F1717 protocol. Screw insertion torque standardized to 8 Nm across all constructs. While lab temperature and humidity were controlled and documented at both facilities, the single test condition (loading rate) represents a limitation relative to the required level. Achieved level 2 reflects this gap; required level 3 not fully met. This factor is flagged as below required level in the credibility summary.",
